OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNetherlands bans mobile    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fphones in classrooms       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Devices including mobile phones are set
OL,6, to be banned from classrooms to stop   
OL,7, them from disrupting learning, the     
OL,8, Dutch government has announced.        
OL,10,FThe initiative is being introduced in  
OL,11,Fcollaboration with schools and is to   
OL,12,Ftake effect at the start of next year. 
OL,14,FThere will be some exceptions,         
OL,15,Fincluding for students with medical    
OL,16,Fneeds or a disability, and for classes 
OL,17,Ffocused on digital skills.             
OL,19,FThe ban is not legally enforceable but 
OL,20,Fmay become so in the future.           
